###Block: Animal Tricks ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Ability Name	Unique Key					Category of Ability		Type			Description																																																															Source Page
Aid			KEY:Animal Trick ~ Aid			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:AnimalTrick	DESC:The animal can use the aid another action to aid a specific ally in combat by attacking a specific foe the ally is fighting.																																											SOURCEPAGE:p.8
Bombard		KEY:Animal Trick ~ Bombard		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:AnimalTrick	DESC:A flying animal can deliver projectiles on command, attempting to drop a specified item that it can carry on a designated point or opponent, using its base attack bonus to determine its attack roll.																															SOURCEPAGE:p.8
Break Out		KEY:Animal Trick ~ Break Out		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:AnimalTrick	DESC:On command, the animal attempts to break or gnaw through any bars or bindings restricting itself, its handler, or a person indicated by the handler. If not effective on its own, this trick can grant the target character a +4 circumstance bonus on Escape Artist checks. The animal can also take certain basic actions like lifting a latch or bringing its master an unattended key.	SOURCEPAGE:p.8
Bury			KEY:Animal Trick ~ Bury			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:AnimalTrick	DESC:An animal with this trick can be instructed to bury an object in its possession.																																																		SOURCEPAGE:p.8
Deliver		KEY:Animal Trick ~ Deliver		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:AnimalTrick	DESC:The animal takes an object to a place or person you indicate.																																																					SOURCEPAGE:p.8
Detect		KEY:Animal Trick ~ Detect		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:AnimalTrick	DESC:The animal is trained to seek out the smells of explosives and poisons, unusual noises or echoes, air currents, and other common elements signifying potential dangers or secret passages.																																	SOURCEPAGE:p.8
Entertain		KEY:Animal Trick ~ Entertain		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:AnimalTrick	DESC:The animal can dance, sing, or perform some other impressive and enjoyable trick to entertain those around it. At the command of its owner, the animal can make a Perform check (or a Charisma check if it has no ranks in Perform) to show off its talent.																						SOURCEPAGE:p.8
Exclusive		KEY:Animal Trick ~ Exclusive		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:AnimalTrick	DESC:The animal takes directions only from the handler who taught it this trick.																																																			SOURCEPAGE:p.9
Flank			KEY:Animal Trick ~ FLank		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:AnimalTrick	DESC:You can instruct an animal to attack a foe you point to and always attempt to be adjacent to (and threatening) that foe.																																												SOURCEPAGE:p.9
Flee			KEY:Animal Trick ~ Flee			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:AnimalTrick	DESC:The animal attempts to run away or hide as best it can, returning only when its handler commands it to do so.																																													SOURCEPAGE:p.9
Get Help		KEY:Animal Trick ~ Get Help		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:AnimalTrick	DESC:With this trick, a trainer can designate a number of creatures up to the animal's Intelligence score as "help." When the command is given, the animal attempts to find one of those people and bring her back to the handler, even if that means journeying a long distance to the last place it encountered the target creature.										SOURCEPAGE:p.9
Hunt			KEY:Animal Trick ~ Hunt			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:AnimalTrick	DESC:This trick allows an animal to use its natural stalking or foraging instincts to find food and return it to the animal's handler.																																										SOURCEPAGE:p.9
Maneuver		KEY:Animal Trick ~ Maneuver		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:AnimalTrick	DESC:The animal is trained to use a specific combat maneuver on command.																																																				SOURCEPAGE:p.9
Menace		KEY:Animal Trick ~ Menace		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:AnimalTrick	DESC:A menacing animal attempts to keep a creature you indicate from moving.																																																				SOURCEPAGE:p.9
Serve			KEY:Animal Trick ~ Serve		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:AnimalTrick	DESC:An animal with this trick willingly takes orders from a creature you designate.																																																		SOURCEPAGE:p.9
Sneak			KEY:Animal Trick ~ Sneak		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:AnimalTrick	DESC:The animal can be ordered to make Stealth checks in order to stay hidden and to continue using Stealth even when circumstances or its natural instincts would normally cause it to abandon secrecy.																															SOURCEPAGE:p.9
Throw Rider		KEY:Animal Trick ~ Throw Rider	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:AnimalTrick	DESC:The animal can attempt to fling a creature riding it to the ground. Treat this as a trip combat maneuver that applies to all creatures riding the animal, and that does not provoke attacks of opportunity.																														SOURCEPAGE:p.9
Watch			KEY:Animal Trick ~ Watch		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:AnimalTrick	DESC:The animal can be commanded to keep watch over a particular area, such as a campsite, and raise an alarm if it notices any sizable or dangerous creature entering the area.																																			SOURCEPAGE:p.9

