Spit						KEY:Llama ~ Spit				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Extraordinary.SpecialAttack									DESC:Once per hour, a llama can regurgitate the contents of its stomach, spitting the foul material at a single target within 10 feet. The target must succeed at a DC 12 Fortitude save or be sickened for 1d4 rounds. The save DC is Constitution-based.																															SOURCEPAGE:p.28
Powerful Bite				KEY:Panda ~ Powerful Bite		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Extraordinary.SpecialQuality									DESC:A panda applies twice its Strength bonus to bite damage.																																																								BONUS:WEAPONPROF=Bite|DAMAGE|STR*2	SOURCEPAGE:p.29
Fatal Gore					KEY:Walrus ~ Fatal Gore			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Extraordinary.SpecialQuality									DESC:A walrus threatens a critical hit with gore attacks on a roll of 19 or 20.																																																					BONUS:WEAPONPROF=Gore|CRITRANGE|1	SOURCEPAGE:p.29
Natural Diver				KEY:Armadillo ~ Natural Diver		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Extraordinary.SpecialQuality									DESC:Armadillos can hold their breath underwater for up to 6 minutes. Their dense armor naturally causes them to sink; they can inflate their stomachs to counter this, accounting for their racial bonus on Swim checks.																																				SOURCEPAGE:p.30
Protective Ball				KEY:Armadillo ~ Protective Ball	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Extraordinary.SpecialQuality									DESC:Some armadillos can roll up into a ball, increasing their natural armor bonus to +3 but decreasing their speed to 0.																																																				SOURCEPAGE:p.30

